UID:a6ba72ce43efa0657468d4b10af78f8f@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate our incredible educators at a special event dedicate
 d to honoring the nominees for the Teacher of the Year Award and the Assis
 tant Teacher of the Year Award. Businesses come together and recognize the
  unique contributions of these outstanding individuals in the tranquil and
  serene setting of a family vineyard nestled on a farm just minutes from d
 owntown Apex. Sponsorships and Donation Opportunities Available - CLICK TH
 E RED REGISTRATION BUTTON ABOVE TO HELP CELEBRATE OUR HARD-WORKING TEACHER
 S: WAYS TO HONOR OUR TEACHERS GOLD SPONSOR $1500 - includes 3 event ticket
 s\, recognition for 4 specific teachers at the event\, and logo on all mar
 keting/signage SILVER SPONSOR $1000 - includes 2 event tickets\, recogniti
 on for 3 specific teachers at the event\, and logo on all marketing/signag
 e BRONZE SPONSOR $750 - includes 1 event ticket\, recognition for 2 specif
 ic teachers at the event\, and logo on all marketing/signage FOOD TABLE SP
 ONSOR $500 - includes 1 event ticket and signage at the 
LOCATION:Apex\, NC
URL:https://business.apexchamber.com/events/details/2026-teacher-appreciat
 ion-event
X-SOURCE:Apex Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
