UID:f6f9146e69fb90ac3e868df9f8628e81@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we bring together our leaders from locally\, region
 ally\, and statewide as they describe the current projects and the future 
 projects that are/will impact our region. This program will be instrumenta
 l for business development leaders and government leaders as we hear how w
 e are building the community for future generations. Confirmed Speakers: C
 olleen Merays - Small Business Manager\, Apex Economic Development Michael
  Haley - Executive Director\, Wake County Economic Development Irena Krsta
 novic - Economic Development Director\, Holly Springs Michael Ebert - Chie
 f Operating Officer\, Economic Development Partnership of North Carolina G
 ary Salamido - President and CEO\, NC Chamber of Commerce Moore Hallmark -
  Vice President & Managing Director\, Regional Gov. Affairs\, U.S. Chamber
  of Commerce
LOCATION:Apex\, NC
URL:https://business.apexchamber.com/events/details/economic-forum-2026
X-SOURCE:Apex Chamber of Commerce
