BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:RIBBON CUTTING : Your Foto Legacy @ Coven Coworking (formerly Blus
 h Cowork)
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T120000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T130000
UID:c915a01e29bd1b96efb4843d59c00fd1@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Ribbon Cutting for Your Foto Legacy Join us on March 19th at 1
 2:00 PM for the ribbon cutting of Your Foto Legacy\, co-hosted by the Apex
  Chamber of Commerce and The Coven Coworking. Celebrate this exciting mile
 stone with light snacks\, giveaways\, and an optional tour of The Coven Co
 working space. About Your Foto Legacy: Your Foto Legacy helps families pre
 serve\, organize\, and digitize their most cherished memories. From printe
 d photos to home movies\, Elena Mock\, Certified Photo Manager\, creates l
 asting keepsakes that tell your family’s story for generations to come.
LOCATION:Apex\, NC
URL:https://business.apexchamber.com/events/details/ribbon-cutting-your-fo
 to-legacy-coven-cowork
X-SOURCE:Apex Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
